title: SimTunes
description:
SimTunes (made by Maxis in 1996) is a PC software where you can make your own musical pictures. Pick some colors and draw plus stamps, choose other Bugz for different sounds, and check out pre-made tunes from the gallery.

This also could be a must-have program for people who want to try their best making music. And don't forget to find a SimTunes tune and/or stamp sharing site online!

If you have problems running SimTunes on Windows Vista, 7, 8, 8.1, or 10, try changing the compatibility settings of the program or use DOSBox.

Thanks for downloading and using this program, anyway!
